  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c513d81420ae4244ea5fa86c11a4a29b, type: 3}
  m_Name: GSWGA_C1_FA_Start_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  lines:
  - "This is it. The big moment. The <i>pi\xE8ce de r\xE9sistance</i> so to speak.
    I am excited! Are you?"
  - When you are ready, please attempt the puzzles. I cannot wait to see this painting
    completed also!
  - These will be puzzles relating to all previous topics you have just practiced,
    so it should come naturally. But again, if you need help, my assistant can offer
    some insight.
